ointed%20managing%20directors%20for%202025.%20He's%20a%20trader%20based%20in%20London.%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Kelly%2FREUTERS%3B%20Courtesy%20of%20Goldman%20Sachs%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20youngest%20member%20of%20Goldman's%20newest%20class%20of%20managing%20directors%20is%2029%20years%20old.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPaulo%20Costa%2C%20promoted%20Thursday%2C%20is%20based%20in%20London%20and%20spoke%20to%20Business%20Insider%20about%20making%20MD.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20trader%20leads%20dividend%20trading%20in%20Goldman's%20synthetic%20products%20group%20in%20EMEA.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20early%20Thursday%20afternoon%2C%20cheers%20celebrating%20Goldman%20Sachs'%20newly%20promoted%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-managing-directors-see-full-list-promotions-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emanaging%20directors%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20been%20mounting%20for%20hours%20throughout%20the%20firm's%20London%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaulo%20Costa%20heard%20the%20trader%20across%20from%20him%20%E2%80%94%20whose%20last%20name%20starts%20with%20an%20X%20%E2%80%94%20take%20the%20call%20he%20had%20been%20hoping%20for.%20He%20presumed%20the%20calls%20would%20be%20rolled%20out%20in%20alphabetical%20order%2C%20and%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20hang%20on%2C%20this%20is%20starting%20to%20feel%20a%20little%20strange%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20last%2C%20the%20call%20came%3A%20he'd%20been%20named%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-partners-advice-new-managing-directors-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emanaging%20director%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%2C%20at%2029%2C%20the%20youngest%20in%20this%20year's%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECosta%20%E2%80%94%20an%20executive%20director%20overseeing%20dividend%20trading%20across%20Europe%2C%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20and%20Africa%20%E2%80%94%20was%20among%20the%20638%20employees%20in%20this%20year's%20Goldman%20MD%20class.%20He%20said%20that%20it%20marked%20the%20culmination%20of%20a%20remarkable%20year%2C%20personally%20and%20professionally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20promotion%20comes%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffounders-wealth-windfall-deals-goldman-sachs-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estrong%20run%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20Goldman's%20equities%20division%2C%20where%20third-quarter%20revenues%20climbed%207%25%20compared%20to%20the%20same%20period%20a%20year%20earlier.%20The%20bank%20cited%20higher%20net%20revenues%20in%20financing%2C%20an%20area%20adjacent%20to%20Costa's%20work%2C%20as%20a%20key%20driver.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeated%20a%20few%20rows%20away%20from%20Costa%20when%20the%20call%20came%20was%20his%20wife%2C%20who%20is%20a%20prime%20broker%20at%20Goldman.%20The%20two%20met%20at%20the%20firm%20in%202018%20and%20married%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20was%20definitely%20the%20first%20person%20that%20I%20spoke%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20once%20he'd%20hung%20up%20the%20phone%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2259b0424b-444f-4954-bf74-6aaf28748684%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20road%20to%20managing%20director%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECosta%20runs%20dividend%20trading%20within%20the%20bank's%20equities%20division%2C%20helping%20big%20investors%20like%20hedge%20funds%20make%20bets%20on%20stocks%20without%20actually%20buying%20them%2C%20using%20financial%20contracts%20that%20move%20with%20share%20prices.%20His%20team%20manages%20the%20dividend%20component%20of%20those%20deals%2C%20ensuring%20that%20when%20companies%20pay%20shareholders%2C%20those%20payouts%20are%20accurately%20reflected%20in%20the%20value%20and%20cash%20flows%20of%20the%20trades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20weathered%20a%20few%20volatile%20markets%2C%20from%20the%20pandemic%20to%20this%20year's%20market%20sell-off%20in%20the%20spring.%20Past%20experiences%2C%20he%20said%2C%20made%20him%20%26quot%3Bmore%20aware%26quot%3B%20of%20how%20to%20approach%20choppy%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20really%20learn%20about%20the%20markets%20and%20the%20inner%20plumbing%20of%20things%2C%20is%20when%20things%20get%20messy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20recalling%20how%20unusual%20trading%20conditions%20during%20the%20COVID%20pandemic%20shaped%20his%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20Portugal%20in%20a%20family%20of%20doctors%2C%20Costa%20said%20his%20parents%20hoped%20he'd%20follow%20in%20their%20footsteps%20and%20pursue%20a%20career%20in%20medicine.%20But%20the%20MD%20title%20he%20clinched%20this%20week%20has%20proven%20just%20as%20satisfying.%20Choosing%20finance%20over%20medicine%20came%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20bit%20of%20a%20shock%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20I%20think%20they're%20happy%20I%20did%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20was%2011%20or%2012%20years%20old%2C%20we%20went%20through%20the%20European%20sovereign%20crisis%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20became%20very%20interested%20in%20how%20the%20financial%20markets%20were%20crashing%20at%20home.%20I%20started%20to%20read%20up%20about%20it%20and%20started%20to%20do%20very%20small%20trades%20when%20I%20was%20that%20age.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECosta%20attended%20the%20University%20of%20Warwick%2C%20where%20he%20served%20as%20the%20equities%20chief%20investment%20officer%20for%20the%20Warwick%20Investment%20Fund%2C%20and%20joined%20Goldman%20as%20a%20summer%20analyst%20in%20the%20securities%20division%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20advised%20those%20who%20might%20want%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-morgan-stanley-denis-coleman-lauren-belmonte-career-advice-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efollow%20his%20path%3C%2Fa%3E%20should%20find%20what%20interests%20them.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20only%20ever%20going%20to%20be%20very%20good%20if%20you%20can%20work%20hard%20at%20something%20for%20a%20very%20long%20time%2C%20perfecting%20your%20craft%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2230344dd7-2df7-4071-adc4-ccdfcad0015b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EInside%20the%20celebration%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20the%20announcement%20became%20official%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Goldman's%20London%20trading%20floor%20was%20already%20buzzing.%20Some%20of%20the%20regional%20leaders%2C%20including%20members%20of%20the%20bank's%20European%20Management%20Committee%2C%20convened%20a%20Champagne%20toast%20for%20new%20MDs%20on%20the%20office's%20eighth%20floor%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20larger-scale%20gathering%20of%20about%20150%20people%20at%20a%20drinks%20venue%20nearby.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20Costa's%20former%20colleagues%20and%20mentors%20appeared%20as%20well%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Lorenzo%20Longo%2C%20a%20former%20Goldman%20colleague%20and%20mentor%20who%20helped%20guide%20Costa%20early%20in%20his%20career.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20almost%20as%20excited%20for%20my%20phone%20call%20as%20my%20wife%2C%26quot%3B%20Costa%20said%20with%20a%20laugh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20now%20he's%20stepping%20into%20the%20role%20they%20once%20held%20%E2%80%94%20a%20leadership%20position%20which%20will%20bring%20new%20responsibilities%20and%20expectations.%20Was%20he%20anxious%20about%20bearing%20those%20new%20duties%20at%20age%2029%3F%20No%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20I%20necessarily%20have%20to%20impose%20myself%20now%20as%20a%20leader%20more%20than%20I%20was%20a%20week%20ago.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20didn't%20deny%20the%20%26quot%3Bgravitas%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20it%20comes%20with.%20%26quot%3BIt%20certainly%20helps%20being%20a%20young%20person%20to%20get%20the%20title%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20conceded%2C%20reflecting%20on%20the%2021-year-old%20version%20of%20himself%20that%20was%20starting%20his%20career%20at%20the%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20already%20beyond%20proud%20of%20working%20here%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20