20in%20Delhi%20or%20Mumbai.%20The%20air%20is%20toxic%20everywhere.%20I%20want%20to%20improve%20my%20own%20quality%20of%20life%2C%20and%20the%20way%20to%20do%20that%20is%20by%20living%20with%20nature%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jai%20tells%20The%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20Delhi%20resident%2C%20he%20often%20visited%20the%20Rajaji%20Tiger%20Reserve%2C%20where%20he%20developed%20a%20deep%20affection%20for%20the%20wildlife.%20Naturally%2C%20when%20it%20came%20time%20to%20find%20a%20place%20to%20settle%2C%20he%20was%20drawn%20to%20the%20area%20that%20had%20become%20almost%20a%20second%20home%20to%20him%20over%20the%20past%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji3-1724833586.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20biosphere%20is%20a%20result%20of%20Jai's%20search%20for%20clean%20air%20and%20pristine%20nature.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji3-1724833586.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji3-1724833586-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji3-1724833586-500x374.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji3-1724833586-768x575.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji3-1724833586-1536x1150.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji3-1724833586-150x112.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-363167%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221198%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20biosphere%20is%20a%20result%20of%20Jai%E2%80%99s%20search%20for%20clean%20air%20and%20pristine%20nature.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20he%20discovered%20a%20stunning%20piece%20of%20land%20nestled%20between%20the%20Rajaji%20Tiger%20Reserve%20and%20the%20Raghati%20river%2C%20complete%20with%20a%20breathtaking%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F338189%2Fbest-national-park-wildlife-safaris-in-winter-adventure-travel-guide-vacation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E300-metre-wide%20riverbed%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20riverbed%2C%20when%20dry%2C%20serves%20as%20an%20elephant%20corridor%20and%20a%20hub%20of%20wildlife%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20says%20that%20being%20there%20feels%20like%20stepping%20into%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Jungle%20Book%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20where%20you%20can%20watch%20animals%20in%20their%20natural%20habitat%20%E2%80%94%20preying%2C%20drinking%2C%20sleeping%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20biosphere%2C%20he%20explains%2C%20is%20a%20micro-environment.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20zone%20of%20life.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20got%20the%20tiger%20reserve%20next%20to%20us%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20pure%2C%20due%20to%20the%20invasion%20of%20non-native%20species%20like%20eucalyptus%20trees.%20We%20are%20working%20on%20creating%20a%20pure%20environment%2C%20growing%20only%20what%20nature%20intended%20for%20in%20this%20particular%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20chasing%20what%20we%20saw%20in%20that%20movie%20Avatar.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20reconnect%20with%20nature%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20acquiring%20the%20land%2C%20which%20was%20then%20covered%20in%20a%20eucalyptus%20forest%20%E2%80%94%20a%20non-native%20species%20%E2%80%94%20the%20major%20challenge%20was%20rewilding%20it.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20the%20land%20was%20used%20for%20agricultural%20purposes%2C%20it%20had%20been%20flattened%20and%20had%20some%205%2C000%20eucalyptus%20trees.%20These%20trees%2