0for%20over%2020%20years%20and%20majorly%20works%20on%20government%20projects%2C%20had%20an%20interesting%20task%20up%20his%20sleeve.%20He%20states%20that%20there%20is%20just%20a%20wall%20that%20separates%20the%20biosphere%20from%20the%20Rajaji%20National%20Park.%20The%20idea%20was%20to%20get%20a%20slice%20of%20Rajaji%20into%20this%20land%2C%20which%20had%20been%20altered%20by%20humans%20for%20their%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20task%20was%20removing%20the%20eucalyptus%20trees.%20The%20second%20task%20was%20creating%20natural%20contours%20that%20existed%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20monsoon%20that%20I%20experienced%20was%20really%20horrifying.%20I%20found%20that%20the%20rainwater%20was%20tapering%20away%20towards%20the%20river.%20Nothing%20was%20being%20retained%20in%20the%20land.%20The%20rain%20was%20taking%20away%20my%20topsoil%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vijay%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9COn%20a%20war%20footing%2C%20we%20created%20the%20natural%20contours%20that%20existed%20to%20ensure%20that%20rainwater%20recharges%20our%20land.%20We%20are%20working%20on%20creating%20magic%2C%20every%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20how%20they%20worked%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F345145%2Fforest-officer-saves-trees-in-chhattisgarh-forest-tiger-reserve-from-encroachers-ifs-varun-jain-timber-poaching%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erewilding%20the%20land%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20says%20that%20they%20took%20cues%20from%20the%20forest%20next%20door.%20They%20observed%20the%20forest%20and%20the%20species%20that%20grew%20there%20and%20worked%20on%20recreating%20the%20broken%20linkages%20between%20different%20species%20and%20creating%20an%20interdependence%20between%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%